  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Retro Soccer is a highly playable well paced arcade action soccer game inspired by soccer games from the 90s like \"Sensible Soccer\" but with a fun low-poly 3d art style. Compete in friendlies, cups or league tournaments and classic tournaments such as the 86 World Cup, Euro 88 and more in single player or against friends in local multiplayer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346740/extras/de153a51ddf74396a2ee1281d0106033.poster.avif?t=1742286626\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346740/extras/de153a51ddf74396a2ee1281d0106033.webm?t=1742286626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346740/extras/de153a51ddf74396a2ee1281d0106033.mp4?t=1742286626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play Modes:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Friendly Match</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cup Tournaments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >League Tournaments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic Tournaments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Single or local multiplayer</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Current features include:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple controls for easy to pickup casual players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Retro style gameplay with a fun visual style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slick passing, Slide tackles, diving headers and rasping shots</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging AI with team skill based on FIFA World Rankings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Change your formations and tactics</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With more features to come during Early Access Development.</p>",
